body:
### Madison May I'm a member of the Class of 2016 at Olin College of Engineering in Massachusetts. I'll be using this space to showcase projects I'm working on and share handy bits of code I run across. ### Recent Projects CoPlay - Collaborative music at it's finest:
https://github.com/madisonmay/coplay Recall - Social media search at your fingertips:
https://github.com/madisonmay/RecallSite
https://github.com/madisonmay/Recall Image2Ascii - Intelligent ascii art generation:
https://github.com/madisonmay/Image2Ascii
